snippet.title: Black Sabbath - "Iron Man" | Haider Ali (Guitar Cover) #Shorts
snippet.description:
“Iron Man” by @Black Sabbath from the album Paranoid — released in 1970 under @Warner Records, and produced by Roger Bain at Regent Sound and Island Studios in London, UK — guitar performance by @Haider Ali.

• Subscribe
https://www.youtube.com/haidertonight?sub_confirmation=1

• Thoughts
Hey folks! It's been ages since I posted any new covers cause you know, life, haha. Anywho, I will be posting new guitar covers consistently. So stay tuned, and thank you for showing up while I was away. I appreciate it. Now, let me tell you how much I love this track. I think I speak for everyone when I say that "Iron Man" probably has the most simple yet, recognizable riffs of all time. The grungy raw feeling of this song is killer. I hope you, folks, enjoy this one. Cheers!
